DataElement.preferredName: Negation Study Subject Administration, Management Performed Study Activity Actual Duration ISO21090.PQ.TIME.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: The completed study level administrative activity that is independent of a study subject. EXAMPLE(S): IRB Approval, site enrollment, FDA audit. The period of time over which the activity is performed.
